Package: VisionSimR
Title: Vision Impairment Simulator for Education and Accessibility
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Dhruv", "Paliwal", , "dhruvp24@iitk.ac.in", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package will take an image and simulates how it appears to a person with a specific eye condition - myopia, hyperopia, astigmatism, presbyopia, or colour blindness. Useful for optometry education, accessibility testing, and helping designers understand how their work looks to people with different vision impairments.
